        <div class="flex items-center justify-center space-x-4 text-gray-400 mb-8">
          <span>August 10 2026</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>{readTime}</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>By {author}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content Toggle based on Published Date -->
  {isPublished ? (
    <article class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <!-- TODO: REPLACE THIS SECTION WITH YOUR ACTUAL BLOG CONTENT -->
          <h2>How Can Busy Madison County Parents Achieve a Back-to-School Cleaning Reset?</h2>
<p><strong>The key to a successful back-to-school cleaning reset is systematic planning and precise execution. For busy Madison County parents, reclaiming a clean and organized home environment is crucial as the school year begins. By implementing a tailored cleaning strategy, you can ensure your home is ready for the new academic year.</strong></p>

<h3>Why a Cleaning Reset Matters</h3>
<p>As the school year kicks off, the hustle and bustle of daily routines can lead to neglect in home maintenance. A cleaning reset is essential to restore order and create a conducive environment for study and relaxation.</p>
<p>Madison County parents know that clutter and disorganization can hinder productivity and increase stress. An organized home provides a calm and efficient space for everyone.</p>

<h4>Step 1: Declutter and Organize</h4>
<p>Start by decluttering each room. Focus on:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Removing items that no longer serve a purpose.</li>
  <li>Organizing school supplies for easy access.</li>
  <li>Creating designated spaces for backpacks and shoes.</li>
</ul>
<p>This step sets the foundation for a systematic cleaning approach.</p>

<h4>Step 2: Deep Clean High-Traffic Areas</h4>
<p>High-traffic areas require special attention. Prioritize cleaning:</p>
<ul>
  <li>The kitchen, where meals are prepared and family gatherings occur.</li>
  <li>The living room, a central hub for relaxation and activities.</li>
  <li>Bathrooms, ensuring they are sanitized and fresh.</li>
</ul>
<p>Our trained cleaning specialists use precision cleaning methods to ensure every surface is spotless.</p>

<h4>Step 3: Establish a Routine</h4>
<p>A consistent cleaning routine is crucial. Consider:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Daily tidying to maintain order.</li>
  <li>Weekly cleaning tasks divided among family members.</li>
  <li>Monthly deep cleaning to address overlooked areas.</li>
</ul>
<p>With a routine, maintaining a clean home becomes manageable, even with a busy schedule.</p>

<h3>Why Choose The Valley Clean Team?</h3>
<p>At The Valley Clean Team, we understand the demands on Madison County parents. Our services are:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Tailored to meet your specific needs.</li>
  <li>Executed with military-precision and accountability.</li>
  <li>Guaranteed to deliver a perfect clean, every time.</li>
</ul>
<p>We go beyond cleaning; we help you restore and maintain a peaceful home environment.</p>

<h3>Transparent Pricing and Local Expertise</h3>
<p>Our transparent pricing starts at $125, ensuring you know exactly what to expect. Being locally owned, we are deeply committed to the Madison community. We bring local expertise and veteran-owned authority to every job.</p>

